_sText:
Remake of the classic zombie mod map zm_droptop_final


Background:
This is a remake of the classic zombie mod map zm_droptop. This version of the map contains several new features including new lighting, better camping spot for humans and overall gameplay fixes.

Support:
Cubemaps, Camping Spots/Barricade areas, 64 Spawnpoints, Optimization

Files:
ZM AN DROPTOP REDUX, ZM AN DROPTOP WINTER (BSP,NAV,.TXT)
